            "body": "I think what happens here is that your first gmt plot command will run as a Cartesian plot since no -J or -fg tells it otherwise.  Then the 10k triggers knowledge of geographic data and this changes the mode from Cartesian to geographic.  If I stick in a -JM15c on the first command then it is all well.",
